(Episode 6)

11
00:02:28,000 --> 00:02:29,880
I can't believe I'm
actually in a relationship.

12
00:02:30,700 --> 00:02:32,100
And it's with Kwon Jungwoo.

13
00:02:40,900 --> 00:02:43,800
(Byun Seung-jin requests a video call)

14
00:02:43,900 --> 00:02:46,270
- Why do we need a video call?
- Hey! My best partner.

15
00:02:46,271 --> 00:02:47,571
Where are you?

16
00:02:47,773 --> 00:02:51,222
I'm just about to head over to you
guys, because I need to talk to Jungwoo.

17
00:02:51,322 --> 00:02:53,381
What a coincidence! Hurry
up and come over, then.

18
00:02:53,481 --> 00:02:55,401
- My sister's treating everyone to coffee.
- Why?

19
00:02:56,200 --> 00:02:57,200
Seung-jin,

20
00:02:57,500 --> 00:02:58,941
Is today your birthday?

21
00:02:59,041 --> 00:03:03,074
No, no, no! My sister's treating everyone
because she just got hired as a broadcaster.

22
00:03:03,075 --> 00:03:05,900
Success, success, total success!

23
00:03:06,600 --> 00:03:09,000
- Haha.
- Success?

24
00:03:18,500 --> 00:03:22,000
Jiwon probably wants an iced Americano,
right? That's why I got it ready in advance.

25
00:03:23,000 --> 00:03:24,500
Thanks, I'll enjoy it.

26
00:03:24,700 --> 00:03:30,200
See, Kwon Jungwoo! No matter how hard you
try, you'll never beat me, the OG superfan.

27
00:03:35,200 --> 00:03:36,200
What's wrong, Seung-jin?

28
00:03:39,200 --> 00:03:41,430
- Are you jealous?
- What are you talking about?

29
00:03:41,800 --> 00:03:43,646
Actually, Jiwon and I...

30
00:03:51,700 --> 00:03:53,900
Your parents must be really happy.

31
00:03:54,120 --> 00:03:55,909
Your sister is great at studying,
and you're really strong in sports.

32
00:03:55,934 --> 00:03:58,669
Your parents probably
don't have anything to worry about.

33
00:03:58,693 --> 00:04:01,000
Such a great personality, must run in the family.

34
00:04:01,400 --> 00:04:05,041
Yeah! Good looks and
brains both run in our family.

35
00:04:05,042 --> 00:04:09,900
Even though my sister has a bit
of a temper, she really is a beauty.

36
00:04:10,000 --> 00:04:11,000
That's how it is, right?

37
00:04:11,120 --> 00:04:12,500
Ah... I see.

38
00:04:14,000 --> 00:04:16,290
But where did Eun-oh run off to?

39
00:04:16,390 --> 00:04:19,697
That guy downed three cups of iced Americano
and ended up running to the bathroom.

40
00:04:19,797 --> 00:04:23,900
This cheapskate if you're looking
for him, just head over to the restroom.

41
00:04:24,100 --> 00:04:28,100
Oh right, Jiwon. Didn't you say you had
something to do at the department office?

42
00:04:29,100 --> 00:04:32,000
- The department office? What for?
- He needs to pick something up.

43
00:04:33,700 --> 00:04:34,700
Right?

44
00:04:40,300 --> 00:04:42,100
If you're bored, do you
want to come with us?

45
00:04:43,200 --> 00:04:44,900
What are you talking about, Jiwon!

46
00:04:45,904 --> 00:04:47,490
It's fine, I have to wait
for that guy.

47
00:04:47,670 --> 00:04:49,908
He's definitely going to want to eat
something again when he gets here.

48
00:04:49,932 --> 00:04:52,416
He's an athlete, but he
never holds back on caffeine.

49
00:04:52,440 --> 00:04:54,300
Well, that's fine. Let's get going.

50
00:05:07,800 --> 00:05:10,300
Drank three cups...

51
00:05:10,500 --> 00:05:11,860
This guy's got something going on.

52
00:05:18,600 --> 00:05:20,760
You said you'd be at the
department office, so I came.

53
00:05:21,500 --> 00:05:22,800
But why sneak in like this?

54
00:05:25,900 --> 00:05:26,900
Hmm...

55
00:05:28,000 --> 00:05:29,000
Why is that?

56
00:05:31,600 --> 00:05:33,400
I just want to be with you.

57
00:05:35,200 --> 00:05:36,700
It's so quiet here.

58
00:05:39,000 --> 00:05:40,320
And it's just the two of us here.

59
00:06:02,900 --> 00:06:05,220
I just wanted to give you a quick kiss.
What are you doing?

60
00:06:06,100 --> 00:06:07,500
Do you want to do something else?

61
00:06:09,300 --> 00:06:13,200
- What?
- Do you want to do something else?

62
00:06:17,600 --> 00:06:18,600
No way.

63
00:06:20,500 --> 00:06:24,100
This is the department office,
people are coming and going, it's risky.

64
00:06:30,900 --> 00:06:33,000
Are you taking me for a fool?

65
00:06:35,300 --> 00:06:36,600
You're really adorable.

66
00:06:38,100 --> 00:06:40,300
How can you be this cute?

67
00:06:55,600 --> 00:06:58,500
Why do I like it so much?

68
00:07:00,400 --> 00:07:03,560
I can barely hold it in anymore. I really
want to show off that we're together.

69
00:07:06,400 --> 00:07:07,400
Me too.

70
00:07:08,200 --> 00:07:09,200
But...

71
00:07:11,100 --> 00:07:12,380
We should be a bit more careful.

72
00:07:16,200 --> 00:07:18,040
How about embroidering
your name on my jersey?

73
00:07:18,600 --> 00:07:20,800
If we use initials, it
won't be too obvious.

74
00:07:21,800 --> 00:07:22,625
How about it?

75
00:07:22,725 --> 00:07:24,600
Aren't you heading off to training camp?

76
00:07:31,600 --> 00:07:32,732
Can I skip it?

77
00:07:32,932 --> 00:07:36,100
- Is it okay if you don't go?
- Of course it's okay...

78
00:07:38,100 --> 00:07:39,500
Too bad that's not the case.

79
00:07:40,600 --> 00:07:41,600
I have to go.

80
00:07:42,700 --> 00:07:47,000
- So you must be really busy today.
- Yeah... I am.

81
00:07:51,000 --> 00:07:54,500
How about... we have
lunch together tomorrow?

82
00:07:57,000 --> 00:07:58,000
Sure!

83
00:08:04,300 --> 00:08:05,300
But...

84
00:08:06,400 --> 00:08:08,200
Class is about to start.

85
00:08:13,000 --> 00:08:15,200
Oh! That's right...

86
00:08:18,000 --> 00:08:19,900
I really have to go now.

87
00:08:28,600 --> 00:08:30,400
I really wish this moment

88
00:08:30,900 --> 00:08:33,400
could last forever.

89
00:08:37,700 --> 00:08:40,299
You must be really hungry. Look!

90
00:08:42,700 --> 00:08:43,700
Hurry up and eat.

91
00:08:54,200 --> 00:08:55,200
Jung-woo.

92
00:08:55,837 --> 00:08:58,533
There are a lot of
people watching us...

93
00:08:58,837 --> 00:09:00,900
It's not like we're about to
kiss, so what's the big deal?

94
00:09:01,900 --> 00:09:04,820
It's pretty common for good friends
to feed each other rice rolls, right?

95
00:09:06,500 --> 00:09:08,800
And there's something I forgot to tell you.

96
00:09:10,100 --> 00:09:11,200
Actually, I...

97
00:09:15,000 --> 00:09:17,600
Because I studied too hard for the exam.

98
00:09:19,000 --> 00:09:20,920
Even moving a finger
feels exhausting right now.

99
00:09:22,300 --> 00:09:23,600
So hurry up and feed me!

100
00:09:39,800 --> 00:09:41,500
Smiling so freely and easily like this.

101
00:09:42,300 --> 00:09:43,800
How long can this last?

102
00:09:48,700 --> 00:09:50,600
Such a blissful moment.

103
00:09:51,200 --> 00:09:52,640
Will it all disappear in an instant?

104
00:09:53,600 --> 00:09:54,600
I'm so scared...

105
00:10:02,600 --> 00:10:05,279
- Let's pull an all-nighter tonight.
- Let's go!

106
00:10:05,379 --> 00:10:07,059
Then let's hit the internet café and play.

107
00:10:07,200 --> 00:10:09,438
Even if we're heading to
the internet café, let's go all out!

108
00:10:09,462 --> 00:10:10,200
Let's go!

109
00:10:11,100 --> 00:10:12,900
I wish you guys would
just disappear already.

110
00:10:16,951 --> 00:10:18,071
What are you thinking about?

111
00:10:18,186 --> 00:10:19,334
What else is there to think
about?

112
00:10:19,787 --> 00:10:23,066
Of course, he's thinking about the feeling
of an ice-cold beer sliding down his throat.

113
00:10:23,100 --> 00:10:26,500
As a die-hard fan, I saw this coming a mile away.
Here, have a drink!

114
00:10:27,700 --> 00:10:31,500
No, Seung-jin, I've already quit
drinking. Now I only drink cola.

115
00:10:32,500 --> 00:10:33,910
Why did you suddenly quit drinking?

116
00:10:34,110 --> 00:10:35,694
Did something happen?

117
00:10:35,695 --> 00:10:36,695
Did something happen?

118
00:10:39,000 --> 00:10:43,000
Hmm... I just thought I'd
take this chance to quit.

119
00:10:44,500 --> 00:10:45,500
What a shame.

120
00:10:46,400 --> 00:10:47,788
You look really
sexy when you drink.

121
00:10:47,812 --> 00:10:50,040
So, how about just not
quitting drinking after all?

122
00:10:50,300 --> 00:10:53,566
Han Jiwon and the word
"sexy" just don't go together at all.

123
00:10:53,590 --> 00:10:56,300
Hold on, why can't we
say Jiwon is sexy too?

124
00:10:57,400 --> 00:11:00,800
