00:21:33,200 --> 00:21:34,700
I totally get it.

249
00:21:36,300 --> 00:21:37,300
Sorry.

250
00:21:39,400 --> 00:21:41,300
I didn't expect you to be scared.

251
00:21:43,600 --> 00:21:44,600
Jiwon.

252
00:21:54,800 --> 00:21:57,899
If you go overseas for
training, what about us?

253
00:21:57,900 --> 00:21:59,980
We probably won't see
each other for a while, right?

254
00:22:02,700 --> 00:22:07,261
I said I wanted a relationship where you take the lead and
guide me. Is that why you're acting this way on purpose?

255
00:22:15,700 --> 00:22:16,900
No way that would happen.

256
00:22:26,200 --> 00:22:27,200
Sorry.

257
00:22:30,600 --> 00:22:32,647
Since this is my first time
being in a relationship,

258
00:22:32,671 --> 00:22:35,040
there are still a lot of things
I don't really understand.

259
00:22:44,100 --> 00:22:45,500
Look at me, Jung-woo.

260
00:22:49,400 --> 00:22:50,840
I'm the one who owes you an apology.

261
00:22:52,600 --> 00:22:53,700
I messed up.

262
00:23:06,100 --> 00:23:07,100
Hey, why are you crying?

263
00:23:13,100 --> 00:23:14,100
I don't know...

264
00:23:29,400 --> 00:23:30,400
Jiwon.

265
00:23:43,100 --> 00:23:44,100
I love you.

266
00:23:51,400 --> 00:23:52,400
I love you too.

267
00:24:28,700 --> 00:24:30,224
(Next episode preview) Traveled overseas
specifically to train for this season.

268
00:24:30,248 --> 00:24:32,688
And on the very first day, you
went and got yourself injured.

269
00:24:33,100 --> 00:24:36,600
Will these malicious comments
end up hurting him again?

270
00:24:39,700 --> 00:24:42,534
The article I showed you turned out to be
Jiwon's public statement clarifying everything.

271
00:24:42,558 --> 00:24:45,567
I never expected to see this post
on Kim Hyo-seok's social media.

272
00:24:45,967 --> 00:24:46,967
Might as well...

273
00:24:47,200 --> 00:24:48,700
Maybe this is actually for the best.

274
00:24:50,300 --> 00:24:51,799
Former national team
player Han Jiwon

275
00:24:51,823 --> 00:24:53,699
and pro basketball star Kwon Jungwoo.
Are they secretly dating?

276
00:24:53,723 --> 00:24:55,476
I always feel like you might
suddenly disappear. Even if I'm

277
00:24:55,500 --> 00:24:57,224
not by your side, it seems
like you'd still be just fine…

278
00:24:57,248 --> 00:24:59,000
I'm not going anywhere.

279
00:25:00,900 --> 00:25:02,580
Let's… give each other some time to think.
